Companion Idle or Move
    Events
        Time - Every 10.00 seconds of game time
    Conditions
        InCinematic Not equal to True
        Or - Any (Conditions) are true
            Conditions
                (Number of units in Companion_Group) Greater than 0
                (Number of units in TamedUnits) Greater than 0
    Actions
        If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
            If - Conditions
                (Number of units in Companion_Group) Greater than 0
            Then - Actions
                Unit Group - Pick every unit in Companion_Group and do (Actions)
                    Loop - Actions
                        Set VariableSet CV = (Custom value of (Picked unit))
                        If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                            If - Conditions
                                IsUnitAlive[CV] Equal to True
                                UnitMoving[CV] Equal to False
                                GCSM_UnitInCombat[CV] Equal to False
                                CompanionDialogueActive Equal to False
                            Then - Actions
                                Unit - Add Wander (Neutral) to (Picked unit)
                                Set VariableSet CompanionUnitIdle[CV] = True
